summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1222, for the improvement of East Jefferson Street from Twenty-ninth Avenue to Thirtieth Avenue, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and constructing concrete sidewalks, under Ordinance No. 13417, and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
